        </div>
      <label class="med-gray h5 mb2 block">Instructor</label>
      <div class="flex underline-link mb3">
        <div class="flex-none mr3">
            <img width="80" src="https://hackdesign.imgix.net/curators/andyhagerman@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails-2.1.4&dpr=2&w=80&h=80&fit=crop&fm=jpeg&auto=format&mask=ellipse&s=91b20df1359f22091f8e5d292fc6978f" alt="Andyhagerman@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails 2.1" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Andy Hagerman</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Co-Founder, 
              <a target="_blank" href="http://thedesigngym.com/">The Design Gym</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm a co-founder at <a href="http://thedesigngym.com/" target="_blank">The Design Gym</a>, based in NYC. We teach a design based methodology for creative problem solving, and put real people's needs at the center of new businesses, services, and products. You can find me <a href="https://twitter.com/andrewhagerman" target="_blank">tweeting here</a> and <a href="http://andyetcetera.tumblr.com/contact" target="_blank">writing here</a>.</p>
        </div>
